02:48.880 --> 02:49.560
Zao Cheng Ge

02:49.920 --> 02:50.240
Morgen

02:50.320 --> 02:50.840
Hast du gegessen?

02:51.000 --> 02:51.480
haben gegessen

02:51.600 --> 02:52.040
OK

02:56.600 --> 02:57.120
Zhou Cheng

02:57.720 --> 02:58.600
Was möchten Sie tun?

02:58.920 --> 02:59.520
Tun Sie es einfach.

03:00.320 --> 03:01.000
